  "htmlContent": "<!--BEHEBES_EMAIL_LAYOUT_START-->\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background:#ffffff;\">\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:40px 16px;\">\n      <table width=\"500\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding:0 0 32px 0;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:0 0 2px 0;font-size:10px;color:#003762;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;\">Verbandsgemeindeverwaltung</p>\n            <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#8fa3b4;font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;\">Otterbach-Otterberg</p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding:0 0 8px 0;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:19px;font-weight:700;color:#003762;font-family:'Segoe UI',Candara,Arial,sans-serif;\">Eskalationsmeldung</p>\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td style=\"padding:0;font-size:14px;color:#1c1c1c;line-height:1.75;font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;\">\n<!--BEHEBES_EMAIL_LAYOUT_BODY_START-->\n<p style=\"margin-top:0;\">Guten Tag,</p>\n    \n      <p>ein Ticket wurde aufgrund eines definierten Ereignisses eskaliert und benötigt kurzfristige Prüfung.</p>\n      <div style=\"background:#fff1ef;border:1px solid #f5c9c3;padding:14px;border-radius:10px;margin:16px 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px 0;\"><strong>Ticket-ID:</strong> {ticketId}</p>\n        <p style=\"margin:0;\"><strong>Eskalationsgrund:</strong> {escalationReason}</p>\n      </div>\n    \n    <div style=\"margin:18px 0 16px 0;\"><a href=\"{ticketUrl}\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#c64631;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;padding:11px 18px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;\">Ticket öffnen</a></div>\n    <div style=\"margin-top:16px;padding:10px 12px;border-radius:10px;background:#f1f6fb;border:1px solid #dbe3f0;color:#35556f;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;\">Falls der Button nicht funktioniert, verwenden Sie bitte den Direktlink:<br/><span style=\"word-break:break-all;\">{ticketUrl}</span></div>\n<!--BEHEBES_EMAIL_LAYOUT_BODY_END-->\n          </td>\n        </tr>\n      </table>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n<!--BEHEBES_EMAIL_LAYOUT_END-->",
